00046 void CHPQuantificationFileWriterTest::WriteTest()
00047 {
00048         ParameterNameValueTypeList params;
00049         ParameterNameValueType param;
00050 
00051         CHPQuantificationData data("CHP_quantification_file");
00052 
00053         data.SetAlgName(L"sig");
00054         data.SetAlgVersion(L"1.0");
00055         data.SetArrayType(L"test3");
00056         data.SetEntryCount(2, 10);
00057 
00058         param.SetName(L"an1");
00059         param.SetValueText(L"av1");
00060         params.push_back(param);
00061         data.AddAlgParams(params);
00062 
00063         params.clear();
00064         param.SetName(L"sn1");
00065         param.SetValueText(L"sv1");
00066         params.push_back(param);
00067         data.AddSummaryParams(params);
00068 
00069 
00070         CHPQuantificationFileWriter *writer = new CHPQuantificationFileWriter(data);
00071         affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetQuantificationData e;
00072 
00073         writer->SeekToDataSet();
00074         e.name = "abc";
00075         e.quantification = 10.0f;
00076         writer->WriteEntry(e);
00077         e.name = "xyz";
00078         e.quantification = 20.0f;
00079         writer->WriteEntry(e);
00080 
00081         delete writer;
00082 
00083         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(1);
00084 
00085 
00086 
00087 
00088         CHPQuantificationData data2;
00089         CHPQuantificationFileReader reader;
00090         reader.SetFilename("CHP_quantification_file");
00091         reader.Read(data2);
00092 
00093         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgName() == L"sig");
00094         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetAlgVersion() == L"1.0");
00095         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetArrayType() == L"test3");
00096         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data2.GetEntryCount() == 2);
00097 
00098         ParameterNameValueTypeList p = data2.GetAlgParams();
00099         ParameterNameValueTypeList::iterator it = p.begin();
00100         param = *it;
00101         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"an1");
00102         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"av1");
00103 
00104         p = data2.GetSummaryParams();
00105         it = p.begin();
00106         param = *it;
00107         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"sn1");
00108         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"sv1");
00109 
00110 
00111         data2.GetQuantificationEntry(0, e);
00112         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.quantification, 10.0f, 0.0001f);
00113         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "abc");
00114         data2.GetQuantificationEntry(1, e);
00115         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.quantification, 20.0f, 0.0001f);
00116         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "xyz");
00117 
00118 }
